-the-gaza-war-transformed-jews-across-the-globe/0000018e-6024-d27e-a7af-7aee16960000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队将在加沙被士兵杀害的人质坟墓上立军事墓碑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-to-place-military-tombstone-on-grave-of-hostage-killed-by-soldiers-in-gaza/0000018e-b765-d50a-a9ff-ff7fe9fb0000</link><description>去年 12 月，阿隆·沙姆里兹 (Alon Shamriz) 与另外两名人质 Yotam Haim 和 Samer Fuad El-Talalka 在加沙逃离绑架者后被枪杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 08:44:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-to-place-military-tombstone-on-grave-of-hostage-killed-by-soldiers-in-gaza/0000018e-b765-d50a-a9ff-ff7fe9fb0000</guid></item><item><title>四名以色列突击队员在加沙南部丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/four-israeli-commandos-killed-in-southern-gaza/0000018e-b6d1-d50a-a1bf-feff25210000</link><description>枪手从隧道中出现后，士兵们在汗尤尼斯地区搜寻恐怖分子时被杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 06:35:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/four-israeli-commandos-killed-in-southern-gaza/0000018e-b6d1-d50a-a1bf-feff25210000</guid></item><item><title>如果没有明确的政治目标，增加加沙援助将无助于以色列军队击败哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/without-declared-goals-increasing-gaza-aid-wont-help-the-israeli-army-defeat-hamas/0000018e-b50d-dc75-afde-f5fd38960000</link><description>以色列国防军在消灭恐怖分子和销毁武器方面取得的战术成功并没有影响加沙战争的结果，如果没有中央政府的分配，增加援助的国际压力也无济于事</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 03:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/without-declared-goals-increasing-gaza-aid-wont-help-the-israeli-army-defeat-hamas/0000018e-b50d-dc75-afde-f5fd38960000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军从加沙撤军；以色列士兵在约旦河西岸枪击事件中受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article-live/israel-strikes-east-lebanon-after-israeli-drone-downed-lebanese-security-sources-say/0000018e-b64a-d43f-a18e-bedffd630000</link><description>以色列国防军称，从黎巴嫩发射的 30 枚火箭落在空旷地区 ■ 以色列国防军突击旅的四名士兵在加沙地带南部的战斗行动中丧生 ■ 黎巴嫩安全部门消息人士称，以色列无人机被击落后，以色列对黎巴嫩中部和东部发动袭击 ■ 英国领导人纪念 10 月以来的六个月7 ■ 周六晚上，以色列各地举行反对政府的抗议活动，五名抗议者在特拉维夫被拒绝服从警察的司机撞倒</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 02:33:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article-live/israel-strikes-east-lebanon-after-israeli-drone-downed-lebanese-security-sources-say/0000018e-b64a-d43f-a18e-bedffd630000</guid></item><item><title>以色列代表团将参加开罗峰会有关加沙人质释放的谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-delegation-set-to-join-cairo-summit-on-gaza-hostage-negotiations-with-hamas/0000018e-b50d-d50a-a9ff-ff1f459a0000</link><description>尽管外交消息人士对哈马斯对其要求采取灵活态度的可能性持悲观态度，但外国消息人士称，内塔尼亚胡决定给予谈判小组有限的决策权，这也阻碍了谈判</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 21:18:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-delegation-set-to-join-cairo-summit-on-gaza-hostage-negotiations-with-hamas/0000018e-b50d-d50a-a9ff-ff1f459a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数万人集会反对内塔尼亚胡政府，要求人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-06/ty-article/.premium/tens-of-thousands-rally-across-israel-against-netanyahus-govt-demand-hostage-deal/0000018e-b4b1-d43f-a18e-befd53c90000</link><description>在特拉维夫，警察和抗议者之间爆发冲突，一名司机拒绝遵守警察命令，冲撞他们，导致五名抗议者受伤。耶路撒冷、海法、贝尔谢巴以及凯撒利亚内塔尼亚胡私人住宅附近也发生了示威活动</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 20:08:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-06/ty-article/.premium/tens-of-thousands-rally-across-israel-against-netanyahus-govt-demand-hostage-deal/0000018e-b4b1-d43f-a18e-befd53c90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 183 天：美国情报警告伊朗袭击，以色列国防军在加沙找到人质尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-183-u-s-intel-warns-of-iranian-attack-idf-recovers-body-of-hostage/0000018e-b451-d43f-a18e-beddcf530000</link><description>美国消息人士警告称，伊朗将使用“无人机和巡航导弹”发动袭击，以回应大马士革袭击 ■ 《纽约时报》：在内塔尼亚胡的通话中，拜登威胁称，如果以色列不采取行动减少平民伤亡，他将停止对以色列的支持 ■ 以色列国防军：以色列人质埃拉德·卡齐尔的尸体在加沙寻回 ■ 以色列国防军：哈马斯官员在加沙南部被杀 ■​​ 战争开始 183 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 17:23:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-183-u-s-intel-warns-of-iranian-attack-idf-recovers-body-of-hostage/0000018e-b451-d43f-a18e-beddcf530000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队从加沙打捞被谋杀的以色列人质埃拉德·卡齐尔的尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-06/ty-article/israeli-army-retrieves-body-of-murdered-israeli-hostage-elad-katzir-from-gaza/0000018e-b393-d50a-a9ff-ff9f85ed0000</link><description>47 岁的卡齐尔于 10 月 7 日在尼尔奥兹基布兹被绑架。以色列国防军在汗尤尼斯的一个墓地发现了他的尸体，并返回以色列。他的妹妹是人质家庭运动的关键人物，她指责政府，称如果不是出于政治考虑，“他本来可以获救”</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 14:19:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-06/ty-article/israeli-army-retrieves-body-of-murdered-israeli-hostage-elad-katzir-from-gaza/0000018e-b393-d50a-a9ff-ff9f85ed0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队射杀一名在其土地上诵读《古兰经》的巴勒斯坦牧羊人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-04-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-troops-shoot-and-kill-a-palestinian-shepherd-reading-the-quran-on-his-land/0000018e-b001-d906-a5cf-b29596ef0000</link><description>三名士兵向坐在羊圈外的牧羊人扑去。他们把他撞倒，然后其中一人近距离射杀了他。法赫·贾比尔 (Fakher Jaber) 是四个孩子的父亲，他被怀疑卷入了一起可能从未发生过的事件</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 13:24:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-04-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-troops-shoot-and-kill-a-palestinian-shepherd-reading-the-quran-on-his-land/0000018e-b001-d906-a5cf-b29596ef0000</guid></item><item><title>流行病、饥荒、未经治疗的伤口：加沙的情况将会变得更糟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/epidemics-famine-untreated-wounds-what-happens-if-the-crisis-in-gaza-continues/0000018e-afe8-d9e9-a9af-effad3950000</link><description>流行病学家警告称，如果加沙人道主义危机持续下去，死亡人数可能达到10万人，甚至超过12万人</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 03:48:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/epidemics-famine-untreated-wounds-what-happens-if-the-crisis-in-gaza-continues/0000018e-afe8-d9e9-a9af-effad3950000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军：以色列无人机在黎巴嫩上空被地对空导弹击落</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-06/ty-article-live/reports-irans-armed-forces-in-high-alert-u-s-prepares-for-significant-iranian-attack/0000018e-b159-d50a-a9ff-ff5ff4c30000</link><description>英国领导人纪念10月7日以来的六个月 ■ 据报道，以色列在黎巴嫩东部发动袭击 ■ 以色列各地举行反对政府的抗议活动 ■ 在特拉维夫，五名抗议者被拒绝服从警察的司机碾压 ■ 哈马斯坚持在释放人质之前停火；代表团将于周日启程前往开罗</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 03:20:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-06/ty-article-live/reports-irans-armed-forces-in-high-alert-u-s-prepares-for-significant-iranian-attack/0000018e-b159-d50a-a9ff-ff5ff4c30000</guid></item><item><title>美国犹太人需要为反以色列情绪盛行的未来做好准备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-06/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/u-s-jews-need-to-brace-for-a-future-where-anti-israel-sentiment-is-prevalent/0000018e-aff7-d906-a5cf-aff7b5430000</link><description>美国犹太人面临的反犹太主义抬头可能会放缓，但反以色列情绪却不会。这些趋势将对犹太人的生活产生什么影响？我们应该如何准备应对对以色列态度的巨大转变？</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 03:15:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-06/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/u-s-jews-need-to-brace-for-a-future-where-anti-israel-sentiment-is-prevalent/0000018e-aff7-d906-a5cf-aff7b5430000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗消息人士：伊朗将直接回应大马士革袭击以“形成威慑”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-06/ty-article/.premium/iranian-sources-iran-will-respond-directly-to-damascus-attack-to-create-deterrence/0000018e-b0b7-d50a-a9ff-febf066f0000</link><description>据美国报道，美国正在为本周可能发生的伊朗“重大”袭击做准备，他们评估这将包括针对以色列外交设施的“大量徘徊无人机和巡航导弹”</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 00:41:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-06/ty-article/.premium/iranian-sources-iran-will-respond-directly-to-damascus-attack-to-create-deterrence/0000018e-b0b7-d50a-a9ff-febf066f0000</guid></item><item><title>南希·佩洛西等 40 名民主党人敦促拜登停止悬而未决的以色列军售和条件援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-06/ty-article/.premium/nancy-pelosi-among-democrats-urging-biden-to-halt-pending-israel-arms-sales-condition-aid/0000018e-b070-d029-a78f-f072b9ac0000</link><description>这位前众议院议长出现在这封信中表明，在持续的加沙战争中，以色列在民主党眼中的地位下降了多少</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 23:05:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-06/ty-article/.premium/nancy-pelosi-among-democrats-urging-biden-to-halt-pending-israel-arms-sales-condition-aid/0000018e-b070-d029-a78f-f072b9ac0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争粉碎了所有假设，让以色列陷入无计可施的境地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/the-gaza-war-shattered-all-assumptions-leaving-israel-scrambling-without-a-plan/0000018e-ad3d-d029-a78f-fd3f6c140000</link><description>多年来主导以色列政策的基本信念在 10 月 7 日崩溃了，而且至今仍未被取代，其结果是，以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突有可能蔓延到整个中东 — — 甚至可能超越中东</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 19:07:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/the-gaza-war-shattered-all-assumptions-leaving-israel-scrambling-without-a-plan/0000018e-ad3d-d029-a78f-fd3f6c140000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 182 天：中央情报局局长预计将前往开罗进行人质释放谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-182-cia-chief-expected-in-cairo-for-hostage-release-negotiations/0000018e-af1e-d9e9-a9af-effe105a0000</link><description>以色列国防军对杀害援助人员的调查发现，这是由于“一系列可避免的错误”造成的，违反了交战规则。 ■ 联合国人权理事会通过决议，呼吁以色列对可能的战争罪行负责。 ■ 由于担心伊朗，以色列使馆关闭报复 ■ 中央情报局局长预计本周末在开罗会见埃及、以色列和卡塔尔对话者 ■ 战争结束 182 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 16:44:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-182-cia-chief-expected-in-cairo-for-hostage-release-negotiations/0000018e-af1e-d9e9-a9af-effe105a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方称人质可能在 10 月 7 日绑架过程中被以色列国防军直升机误杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/idf-says-hostage-likely-mistakenly-killed-by-army-helicopter-during-abduction-on-oct-7/0000018e-ae81-d9e9-a9af-eff3a1730000</link><description>以色列国防军的一份声明称，有证据表明，哈马斯恐怖分子用来劫持人质的车辆被空军击中，埃弗拉特·卡茨死亡。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 15:40:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/idf-says-hostage-likely-mistakenly-killed-by-army-helicopter-during-abduction-on-oct-7/0000018e-ae81-d9e9-a9af-eff3a1730000</guid></item></channel></rss>